data.description: If you've been dreaming of a cozy cabin nestled in the trees in the Smoky Mountains, this is it! At just over 1550 sq ft, this home offers mainlevel living with an open concept layout with kitchen, dining, living room with gas fireplace, bedroom, full bath & a great outdoor deck all on the main level. The 2story wall of windows provides so much natural light and views of the beautiful forest from the main level and the upstairs loft which features another bedroom withfull bath. The lower level also offers an additional living area and storage space as well as a 2nd deck. You'll also love additional features such as the metal roofand living in a gated community with full time security & community pool! Put your own special touch on this cabin and enjoy memories for years to come!
